Titolo: Perfect Weapon (video game)

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: Perfect Weapon is an action-adventure video game developed by Gray Matter and published by ASC Games. The game released on November 21, 1996 for PlayStation and February 1997 for Windows 95. Marketed as "Tekken 2 meets Resident Evil", it met with mediocre reviews. During development, the game was scheduled for release on May 1997 for the Sega Saturn, but the port was cancelled. The game was re-released on March 25, 2010 in North America for the PlayStation Network as a PSOne Classic and can be played on PSP, PS3, and PSVita.